Learners from Gateway Combined Christian School from Barberton were part of the Southern African Christian School’s Sports Association Mpumalanga archery team at the Archery Nationals that were hosted in Ermelo. Read More: Gateway Christian School learners shine at prestige awards ceremony Gateway learners did exceptionally well with the following results: • Boys’ u/9 – Ruan Fourie (gold) • Boys’ u/11 – Diehahn Strauss (silver) and Monde Majola (bronze) • Girls’ u/13 – Shanrè Ehlers (gold) and Daniella Strauss (silver) • Boys’ u/19 – Juan Fourie (bronze)